Future Earth Survey on Health Priorities
--------------------------------------------
The Future Earth platform for global sustainability research is conducting a survey on priorities for its health initiatives. We encourage you to share your input and pass the survey on to others in your country, organization, or community of practice who may be interested. To learn more and participate in the very short survey, please visit:

http://www.futureearth.org/news/take-survey-health-priorities-under-future-earth.

--
Peter Daszak and William B. Karesh
EcoHealth Alliance and the Future Earth Health Knowledge-Action Network
Co-Chairs, International Project Office of the Future Earth Future Health core project

Catherine Machalaba
EcoHealth Alliance and the Future Earth Health Knowledge-Action Network
Science Officer, International Project Office of the Future Earth Future Health core project
